{"tid":2034461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人手置頂 每日任務 Twitter + 聯署","createTime":"2020-05-25T08:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:45:47.000Z","uid":321895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"425f0f332fa4f326fb631b0b7863b6e8d8f89d95","tid":2034461,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好多人都唔識國際戰線可以點打</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聯署</strong></span><br />\n網址：<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3sIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=8b2b943d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a><br />\n<br />\n網頁介面：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmW17nH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmW17nH.png&h=d4b19164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">步驟：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1）設定個人資料 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">僅需在首次使用時設定</span><br />\n<br />\n用戶設定：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FopnRP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFopnRP6.png&h=12227ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2） 開始聯署</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nwv6y4t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwv6y4t.png&h=3fb561c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">按一下 「聯署」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3）到Email Box度Confirm</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">必須確認confirmation email才算完成</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter戰線</strong></span><br />\n網址：<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3sIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=06d6809f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">步驟：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1）輸入  /start<br />\n<br />\n2）輸入 /task<br />\n<br />\n3）按 /task1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4）按次序進入twitter 連結<br />\n<br />\n5）Like + Retweet + CM<br />\n<br />\n6) 做曬task 1 task 2 task 3</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>記得每日都要做</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">光復香港 <br />\n一齊努力</span></ins></em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b08a5d8e0fe6c8a4415d32c995b67054c11c1c2d","tid":2034461,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abc2d0710cfa8f9a7a8abfa51996095b8135eca4","tid":2034461,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cdb5807596cd8900bd39fabd6376a446e7c5c30","tid":2034461,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:54:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1aac3e6c239bba3935fe4d372196f2cc5fde4f09","tid":2034461,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48d6229fbb2c553a08db2f4c6368ba5b122fd2a","tid":2034461,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:55:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caf1f143a2cc2a942a0f6db7ac8a734e3abe609a","tid":2034461,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee69786ddb45fc2770f51951ab70561e5b0ca828","tid":2034461,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"［突發］有人起ig搞左個「#全城㩒美元」挑戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br /